 《僵尸肖恩》将重返影院庆祝上映 20 周年https://www.nme.com/news/film/shaun-of-the-dead-is-returning-to-cinemas-for-its-20th-anniversary-3778087?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=shaun-of- 《死者之魂》重返电影院庆祝其二十周年纪念日Chris EdwardsThu, 25 Jul 2024 16:21:49 +0000 Film NewsNewsComedy https://www.nme.com/?p=3778087 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科尔内托三部曲" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该影片已采用杜比全景声 (Dolby Atmos) 和 Vision 重新制作</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/shaun-of-the-dead-is-returning-to-cinemas-for-its-20th-anniversary-3778087">《僵尸肖恩》即将重返影院庆祝其上映 20 周年，</a>该海报首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科尔内托三部曲" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/T0JFT4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特 (Edgar Wright)</a>宣布<em>《僵尸肖恩》</em>将在影院重新上映，以庆祝这部僵尸喜剧问世 20 周年。</p><p>这位导演于周四（7 月 25 日）在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C92MZIYo5uY/?igsh=MXI5N2JseGZ2d290dw%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上分享了这一消息，确认这部由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simon-pegg">西蒙·佩吉</a>和尼克·弗罗斯特领衔主演的电影已采用杜比全景声和杜比视界重新制作，将于 8 月下旬登陆美国影院和英国影院。九月底在爱尔兰电影院上映。</p><p> “二十年前， <em>《僵尸肖恩》</em>的全球上映永远改变了我的生活，”赖特在帖子开头说道。 “从那时起，它的受欢迎程度一直令人难以置信，这很大程度上要归功于热情的球迷，他们高举板球棒来支持它。</p><p> “现在，当我们以全新的杜比全景声 (Dolby Atmos) 和视界 (Vision) 重制版庆祝该片诞生 20 周年之际，我非常兴奋地希望每个人都能在大银幕上再次体验它，就像它一直以来的观看方式一样：大屏幕，声音很大，上面有很多红色。</p><p> “ <em>《僵尸肖恩》</em>将于 8 月重返美国影院，9 月重返英国影院，庆祝上映 20 周年。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C92MZIYo5uY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C5